[This is a summons from the Jax Trust in Cutthroat Harbor.

Complete this quest to unlock daily quests from the Jax Trust.]

I'm Jax, master of the Jax Trust.

I've heard you've been very helpful for our business, so I wanted to thank you in person.

I treat my business like a family, and now you're officially a "friend of the family."

When we profit, all of Cutthroat Harbor profits. I look forward to many great things from you.
